Once upon a time, there lived three pigs with their mama.
One day, the pigs left home to make their own homes.
On the way, the first piggie stopped by some sticks. "I will make my house from sticks!".
THe second piggie stopped by a shop of straw. "I will build my home from straw!"
The third piggied stopped by a brick shop and bought bricks.
"I will make my home out of bricks!"
All three piggied headed out to make their homes.

The first piggie made his home from sticks.
The second piggie made his home from straw.
The second piggie made his home from bricks.

